text: Senate elections were held in Cambodia on 25 February 2018 after being postponed from 14 January 2018.http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2017-10/27/c_136709880.htm For the first time, the Senate and parliamentary elections occurred in the same year. The result was a victory for the CPP, which won all 58 seats. King Norodom Sihamoni nominated Princess Norodom Arunrasmy and Oum Somanin to the Senate.http://www.phnompenhpost.com/national-politics/cpp-claims-all-58-seats- grabs-senate ==Results== ==References== Category:2018 in Cambodia Category:2018 elections in Asia 2018
title: 2018 Cambodian Senate election
